  "type": "object",
  "x-planetary-semantic-invariants": [
    "Verify Ed25519 and the bound request_sha256/inventory_sha256 before reservation.",
    "Authority expires at not_before + ttl_seconds; renewal_sequence must increase and renewals_remaining must not increase.",
    "For a renewal of lease_id, fencing_token and renewal_sequence strictly increase; consumers accept only the exact active digest/token revision.",
